Where can I get a code to activate this?

Your team is given one as part of the kickoff kit each season. You can skip the activation steps to just run the Drive Station even in a trial mode.

It’s a green cardboard packet envelope with a big white N on it.

Edit: if you can’t find that Ni has a process for finding your serial number as of 2020 in your lead mentors firstInspires dashboard.

knowledge.ni.com
